Content:
The next shopping platform is the missing step between existing e-commerce systems and (far from now) implementation of augmented reality desired experience.
With my new shopping platform, several issues will be achieved:
- increased sales volume: because my concept take advantage of human behavior (seeing is shopping);
- ads powered but avoiding to be annoying;
- best user experience and user interface ever designed;
- comprehensive product information for better selection;
- powerful social-commerce integration.
